  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>But at my\n        back ...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>An ironic distortion of Andrew Marvell's \"To His\n        Coy Mistress\", lines 21-22: \"But at my back I\n        always hear/ Time's wingèd chariots hurrying near. Cf.\n        also l. 196 (NA)</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Mistress_AM.htm\">Andrew\n                Marvell<i>, </i>\"To His Coy Mistress\"</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
